review: Since I am visiting Dr. Ilin Kinimi from last three months, I am happy with the treatment and diagnosis method which includes only the necessary tests. The results have fulfilled the need and expectations. But the management has to be improved a lot in staffing and facilities. There are no proper guidance towards the formalities hence the waiting period also exceeds.

Illin we go for our 10 yrs old whenever our local paediatrian is not able to solve his cough problem. She handles situation very well n gives lot of time to understand the patient. She is a sincere doctor n polite too.She is intelligent doctor. She sets a routine like steam , nebulization , medicine which help in recovery.
Thank you doctor that my child is back to normal routines. You were very courteous and attended to the point.

I am more than happy for consulting her. The way she approached was impressive and she treated my daughter with extreme care. The hospitality is good as well. The waiting time was not beyond 20 minutes in my experience.
I think doc should explain problem more accurately and extensively. morever she was not at all friendly..

From the last two months, I am consulting her. She has been very cooperative. I am very happy with her assistance. The services are excellent. I have never waited more than 15 minutes for my consultation. I will highly recommend the doctor.

The treatment is under progress. Almost three months have completed now. As of now everything is fine. I am happy with the doctor. As they follow first in first out rule, the wait time directly depends on the number of patients in the queue.
Any advance treatment of  cystic fibrosis in your hospital so please ability this deses consulting Doctor

For my child's routine health check-up, we have consulted him. She approached in a pleasing way and interacted very well. We are extremely satisfied with the consultation. The hospitality was also appreciative. The waiting period was not more than 30 minutes. Everything was quite comfortable. I will surely recommend the doctor.

I am only concerned about the waiting time as I have to travel from a long distance and carrying a child along is really a difficult part. A cut in the wait time might help a lot. As of now, she has prescribed some medications with which we have obtained a good result but the treatment is yet to be continued. We have multiple sessions ahead and hope for the best.
